                <note rend="inline" type="source">211.68/158: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Greece</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Shantz</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-09-29T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >September 29, 1937—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>36. Your 63, September 2, 2 p.m. In view of signing of protocol you should, if
                    you have not already done so, withdraw notice of abrogation given pursuant to
                    Department’s 55, November 4, 1933, 11 a.m.<note n="22" xml:id="d322fn22">Not
                        printed.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
